1. *Puške* su bile glavno oružje u Drugom svetskom ratu. (Guns were the main weapon in World War II.)
2. Pripadnik vojske izgubio je *pušku* tokom borbe. (A soldier lost his gun during the battle.)
3. *Puškom* je pucao u vazduh da bi upozorio lovce da je kraj dana. (He fired a gun into the air to signal the end of the day for hunters.)
4. Lovci su nosili svoje *puške* na leđima tokom celog lova. (Hunters carried their guns on their backs throughout the entire hunt.)
5. Policijski službenik je zaplenio nekoliko *pušaka* tokom racije. (A police officer seized several guns during a raid.)
6. Vojska je morala da napusti svoje *puške* kada su se povlačili iz grada. (The army had to abandon their guns when retreating from the city.)
7. Bilo je čudno videti devojku sa *puškom* u rukama. (It was strange to see a girl with a gun in her hands.)
8. Pronađeno je više od deset *pušaka* u skladištu oružja. (More than ten guns were found in the weapons warehouse.)
9. Njegov deda je nasledio *pušku* od svog oca. (His grandfather inherited a gun from his father.)
10. *Puške* su bile skladištene u podrumu zgrade. (Guns were stored in the basement of the building.)